Come on. ls he really that good-looking?
其实，他真有那么英俊吗？

883
01:01:21,152 --> 01:01:23,587
Are you kidding? He's gorgeous!
开什么玩笑，他绝对能迷倒众生

884
01:01:23,722 --> 01:01:27,090
He has a face that looks like it was carved by angels.
他的脸那么棱角分明

885
01:01:27,226 --> 01:01:28,716
- Oh. He sounds dreamy. - You know...
