886
01:01:29,496 --> 01:01:33,024
shockingly, this isn't making me feel any better.
可惜我一点感觉都没有

887
01:01:35,806 --> 01:01:39,470
Look, guys. lt's for the best.
这样对大家都好

888
01:01:39,644 --> 01:01:44,448
Mom and Dad approve, and Fiona gets the man she's always dreamed of.
妈妈爸爸同意了 费欧娜得到她梦寐以求的人

889
01:01:44,551 --> 01:01:45,745
Everybody wins.
大家都能赢

890
01:01:47,689 --> 01:01:48,951
Except for you.
除了你

891
