我害怕费欧娜并不 那么钟情于白马王子

899
01:02:22,538 --> 01:02:26,566
- FYl, not my fault. - No, of course it's not, dear.
- 其实，也不能怪我 - 当然不会

900
01:02:26,644 --> 01:02:30,582
l mean, how charming can l be when l have to pretend l'm that dreadful ogre?
