908
01:02:55,218 --> 01:02:57,413
l can't. l won't do it.
我不能，我不会那样做

909
01:02:57,521 --> 01:02:59,819
Oh, yes, you will.
你会的，如果你记得

910
01:02:59,925 --> 01:03:02,588
lf you remember, l helped you with your happily ever after.
我成全了你的今生幸福

911
01:03:02,728 --> 01:03:06,187
