我也能轻易地拿走

912
01:03:06,334 --> 01:03:09,566
ls that what you want? ls it?
你要这样吗？

913
01:03:11,041 --> 01:03:13,066
- No. - Good boy.
- 不 - 好孩子

914
01:03:13,477 --> 01:03:14,808
Now, we have to go.
我们要走了

915
01:03:15,146 --> 01:03:17,307
l need to do Charming's hair before the ball.
