Oh. Thank you, Mother. [Donkey] Mother?
- 谢谢，母亲! - 母亲？

919
01:03:26,629 --> 01:03:29,224
Um... Mary! A talking horse!
玛丽!会说话的驴子!

920
01:03:29,366 --> 01:03:30,355
The ogre!
