992
01:07:47,600 --> 01:07:50,695
Gingy! Pinocchio! Get us out of here!
姜饼人!小木偶 快救我们出去!

993
01:07:56,845 --> 01:07:58,745
Fire in ze hole!
洞里有火！

994
