Boom! That's what l like to hear. Look who's coming around!
这样讲话就对了 看看这下谁终于想通了

1013
01:09:17,026 --> 01:09:21,888
lt's impossible! We'll never get in. The castle's guarded. There's a moat and everything!
不可能，我们进不去的 城堡有守卫，而且还有护城河!

